<div class="" >
    <div class="main-bar">
      <%= link_to "cocktails", root_path %>
      <%= link_to "share", root_path %>
      <%= image_tag "logo.png", alt: "logo", width: "220px" %>
      <%= link_to "what?", root_path %>
      <%= link_to "who?", root_path %>
    </div>
  <div class="background-cover">
    <div class="cover-container">
        <div class="panel-01">
        </div>
        <div class="panel-02">
          <h1 class="headline">Welcome to your online repertoire for classic and custom <span class="highlight">cocktail recipes</span> from all over the world!
          <%# link_to "Share your recipe with us", new_cocktail_path %></h1>
          <%= image_tag "blob_green02.png", alt: "blob", width: "400px" %>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="break">
  <div class="text-break">
    <div class="cover-container">
      <div class="panel-03">
        <h1>What<br> is this about?</h1>
        <%= image_tag "blob_green03.png", alt: "blob", width: "150px", class: "blob-what-green" %>
        <%= image_tag "blob_pink03.png", alt: "blob", width: "80px", class: "blob-what-pink" %>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-04">
        <p>What is this web site all about? How did you get here?
          Maybe subconsciously you were thirsty for a drink!
          <br><br>
          Free Pour Cocktail is a place where you can find
        the perfect recipe for the drink you're looking for.
        It can be as simple as a classic Daiquiri or discover
        someone else's creation! What ever mood you're in, you'll find something to match it here.

        <br><br>

        Enjoy and drink responsibly. Cheers!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="banner-image">
  </div>
</div>

